<br>
1)  I have bad days too, and if your request for a port isn't as nice as you can make it, you might get a nasty response from me.  I apologize, but bad day+bad tell=bad response.<br>
<br>
2) Even if i'm having a bad day, my response is usually sorry, but i'm not available for ports ATM.  I might even include a reason why, because I think you might actually care.  if your response is &quot;ok cool, I understand.  best of luck to you&quot;  you run a VERY high chance of getting a tell &quot;ahh well, i'm at xxx loc, if you can get here before I gotta skedaddle, i'll send you&quot; and I DO send a tell amply before I leave to said person after that letting them know time is running short for me.<br>
<br>
Evil response?  gets you /ignore motard<br>
<br>
and telling me you have a wizard and that 1.5pp for a fragment is nothing is never, ever going to endear me to you in any way shape or form.<br>
<br>
my personal pet peaves?<br>
<br>
1) Lying.  if your paying, pay.  if you can't, say so.  I will be annoying to you if you lie to me.  if you don't lie to me, you run a good chance of getting a port anyway.  I care more about being lied to about the 100pp than getting the 100pp.  I normally refuse payment<br>
<br>
2) Don't assume because you've been sitting around for an hour shouting for port and finally decide to say 100pp that thats the reason i've sent you a tell saying ok.  Maybe I was busy, and am now available, maybe I was AFK, maybe I just got into the zone... don't be nasty.  I'm one of those annoying people that bases what I do on other peoples reactions.  <br>
<br>
I don't generally tell you &quot;no charge&quot; for the port until you put it up into the window... I like to know that you feel my time is worth the money, and that you appreciate that i'm doing it for free.  I also like to know that you think i'm some money-grubbing evil person cause I want the 20pp that you said you would pay (at the least) when you said &quot;WTB port&quot;  - doesn't matter that I would refuse the payment, and that I just wanted to see that your not lying.  Annoying, I know.  but hey, I gotta get my warm fuzzy's somehow.<br>
<br>
random person who's never posted here before.<br>
<br>
Taranious, Lvl 52 Wizard, Xegony, Tainted Twilight <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukwinic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kwinic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/12/02 3:46:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21993.topic&index=82>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.karnij.com/images/kwinic/littlekwin.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to get a port.</span><hr size=1> Here here Taranious <p><table border="0" width="111"><tr><td><img src="http://www.karnij.com/images/kwinic/kvsct.jpg"></td><td valign="top" nowrap style="filter:glow(color=#5566CC" strength="2");font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt'"><center><font Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif color=#22DD33>* Kwinic Yoegh'ilrymmin *</a><BR>-----------------------------<BR> Member of The Kindred<BR>Nihilist of the "Gods"<BR>Wizard of Drinal<BR>Proud Erudite<BR>AoE Addict </font></center></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showPrevMessage?topicID=21993.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showNextMessage?topicID=21993.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21993.topic&index=82><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.emailToFriend?topicID=21993.topic><img src=